              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Music</td>
                <td><span class="grade grade-b">Good</span></td>
                <td>Learning guitar, regular practice needed</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Debate & Drama</td>
                <td><span class="grade grade-a">Excellent</span></td>
                <td>Outstanding public speaking skills</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <!-- Teacher's Remarks -->
          <div class="remarks-section">
            <div class="remarks-title">üìù Class Teacher's Remarks:</div>
            <div class="remarks-text">
              Rajesh is an excellent student who consistently demonstrates
              strong academic performance and a positive attitude. He shows
